family: Sail

designer: LatinoType

approved: true
description: <p>Sail is a Didot script for \
  headline, display and poster uses. A fresh air comes to \
  all the glyphs, its windy uppercases are especially \
  suited for display texts and web navigation. Elegant \
  swashes and a clean lowercases also make it suitable \
  for larger paragraphs.</p>

font.Sail-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Sail-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

